    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skills",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_2334909104406146735.png",
                "id": "talent41223",
                "key": "Shattering Waves ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Shattering Waves "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. This character deals +1 DMG for every 3 additional max HP provided by <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Insatiable Appetite</span> (Max +4.) After this, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span> 1 card from your Hand with the highest original Elemental Dice Cost.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/923db325e73849fb31b138dfdd1a0cab_4882010859286676194.png",
                "id": "talent8940",
                "key": "Starfall Shower",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Starfall Shower"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby. Summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dark Shadow</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/dec2f5cea15b6652638355fb66ef2d98_9005227972467306823.png",
                "id": "talent35465",
                "key": "Ravaging Devourer",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Ravaging Devourer"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When battle begins, create 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Deep Devourer's Domain</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Deep Devourer's Domain</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Combat Status</span><br>Cards you have <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span>ed or used for <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tune</span> will be consumed.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">For every 3 cards consumed</span>, the All-Devouring Narwhal gains 1 extra Max HP. If there are at least 2 Cards amongst these that have the same original Elemental Dice Cost, gain another 1 extra Max HP. If all 3 Cards have the same original Elemental Dice Cost, gain yet another 1 extra Max HP.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/edd2da5186218246a20f5b0d52d2c634_7103634465262430877.png",
                "id": "talent96601",
                "key": "Insatiable Appetite",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Insatiable Appetite"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When played:</span> Gain \"Attack Power\" equal to the Elemental Dice Cost of the devoured card with the highest Cost, and gain <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> based on the number of devoured Cards with said Cost.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase and when you declare the end of your Round:</span> Deals <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro DMG</span> equal to \"Attack Power.\"<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When your active character takes DMG:</span> Reduce DMG taken by 1, then this card's <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s)</span> -2.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7351364317876849891.png",
                "id": "talent50449",
                "key": "Dark Shadow",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/bc781100ebefe81947d3fac533aaed65_4651125597590540355.png",
                "title": "Dark Shadow"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG+1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_8740590846529305916.png",
                "id": "talent56751",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Electro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 for this instance, the target is forcibly switched to the next character</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_4687959480780597835.png",
                "id": "talent2255",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Discard</span></strong><br>Use Action Cards or Character Skill effects to Discard Action Cards from Hand or Deck.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong><br>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\"><br>Tune</span></strong><br>Discard Action Cards from Hand to initiate Elemental Tuning</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/15/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3106726858035899537.png",
                "id": "talent21319",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
