                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meow.\" \"Most cats are afraid of falling into any water, never mind the great lakes or the ocean. And the leviathans lurking in the depths... Knowledge of their existence alone would make them turn tail and flee on the spot.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(204, 191, 173)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Special Rule: This opponent engages in a Duel with you rather than an Adventure Challenge. The All-Devouring Narwhal is immune to Frozen, Stun, and Petrification, and starts with the Talent Card \"Lightless Feeding\" equipped. It will also Discard 1 card from its Hand at the start of each Round.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Opposing Lineup",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
